Currency Converter
A JavaFX desktop application that converts currencies in real-time using the ExchangeRate-API.
Features

ğŸŒ Real-time currency conversion
ğŸ’± Support for 10 major currencies (USD, EUR, GBP, JPY, AUD, CAD, CHF, CNY, INR, MXN)
ğŸ¨ Clean and intuitive user interface
âš¡ Fast API integration with proper error handling
ğŸ§ª Tested with Boomerang API client

Prerequisites

Java 21 or higher
Maven
Internet connection (for API calls)
ExchangeRate-API key (free tier available)

Installation

Clone or download this project
Get your API key:

Go to https://www.exchangerate-api.com/
Sign up for a free account
Copy your API key


Configure the API key:

Open src/main/java/com/currencyconverter/service/ExchangeRateService.java
Replace YOUR_API_KEY_HERE with your actual API key:



java   private static final String API_KEY = "your_actual_api_key_here";

Build the project:

bash   mvn clean install
Running the Application
Option 1: From IDE

Open the project in IntelliJ IDEA or Eclipse
Right-click on Main.java â†’ Run

Option 2: From Command Line
bashmvn javafx:run
Option 3: Run JAR file
bashjava -jar target/converter-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar
